# Normalize all text files to LF in the repo and on checkout,
# regardless of OS. Git auto-detects binary; the rules below are
# explicit safeguards for common asset formats.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary assets
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.icns binary
*.webp binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
*.ttf binary
*.eot binary
*.otf binary
